messages.text: We’re not supposed to keep secrets from each other.
Is there something you want to tell me?
Fine. I guess you heard the “rumor.”
How could I not? Why didn’t you just tweet it out to the whole school?
You’re not really going to do this, are you?
The captain of the football team? Tyler?
Look, he’s the one who started it.
By saying if he was going to take someone’s virginity…
How did you even find out?
He said it after practice. Anthony told Sophia.
Sophia told Ashley and Ashley told me after choir.
So your just going to have sex with him?
Yes. I’m ready. And who better than the captain of the football team?
We pass each other in the halls.
One time he smiled at me. At least I think it was me. I was in a group.
I just want to get it over with.
But shouldn’t you choose someone you know? Someone you trust?
That’s sweet, but I’d rather choose someone… Popular :)
So you’re really going to go through with it tonight at the party?
And Ethan, I know you want to do what’s right for me. But don’t get in my way.
Come hang out with me. I look like a loser.
I don’t know. They don’t come to these parties.
Do you think he bailed on me?
Did you text him about this!?!?
No! But he knows. I purposely told Ashley how I was going to seduce him.
It should’ve gotten back to him.
I’m going to grab a drink.
WAIT. There’s a note on the fridge.
It’s from Tyler. It says to meet him on the porch swing.
SEE. I told you he got the message :)
It says to check my car.
Maybe he’s trying to be romantic.
You don’t have to do this.
Yes, I DO! Everyone knows now. I have to.
This one wants me to drive somewhere!
It says to meet him at the pier.
There’s only one reason people go there.
I wasn’t picturing it like this. In a car.
What if I kick it into neutral and we roll in the water?
Think that’s probably the least of your worries.
You don’t have to do this.
There’s something I need to tell you.
I’ll just stop somewhere on the way.
Well, it’ll probably be all right, right?
Wait. I see Ashley. Hold on.
Oh, fine. And she had plenty of supplies ;)
What if for your first time
You could be with someone who loved you? Who cared about you?
I know how you feel, ok?
I would never risk our friendship.
I think there’s someone else inside!!!
Look, there’s something I have to tell you.
Yes. I love you. As a friend.
The person you saw making out with Tyler was me.
We’ve been together for almost six months.
Neither one of us is ready to, you know, make it public.
He said if he was going to take any girl’s virginity it would be you...
because the other guys put him on the spot and he knows we’re BFFs.
So he doesn’t want to have sex with me…
We’re trusting with you with this secret.
And you have to tell everyone you had sex.
SO I’M GOING TO FAKE LOSE MY VIRGINITY???
That’s how I hear it usually is.
